These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, van, roller
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bongani, montecristo
1. the bongani-smoker is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the montecristo-smoker and the person driving the van##2
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Transport      | van | roller | airplane |
| Cigar   | bongani     | dunhill    | montecristo   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, raspberry, mango
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, tulip
1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person who growstulip is between the person who growszinnia and the person eating kiwi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Food   | kiwi    | mango        | raspberry |
| Flower     | rose | tulip | zinnia         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, jazz, r&b
1. the fan blues is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is between the fan jazz and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian     | japanese |
| Music-Genre        | jazz  | r&b | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar, old-henry
House: tower, futuristic, palace
1. the prince-smoker is the tower house##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the futuristic house and the tower house##2
3. the palace house is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | old-henry     | prince |
| House           | futuristic | palace | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different games are played: go, poker, bridge
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, family, martial-arts
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching family movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Game   | poker | bridge     | go |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts    | fantasy | family    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cauliflower, garlic
3 different pets are kept: bird, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the bird is between the person eating garlic and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Food   | artichoke  | cauliflower   | garlic        |
| Pet         | horse | bird | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, singing, gardening
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, trike
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby          | singing  | sudoku  | gardening |
| Transport   | ship | motorbike | trike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, june
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | june   | april  | december  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | fanta | lemonade |

 #################################

 
