.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, filmmaking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, action, western
1. the person watching western movies is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person watching documentary movies##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | fishing | drawing      | filmmaking      |
| Movie-Genre       | action  | western | documentary |

