.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, go
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, train, bike
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the train##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | scrabble   | go   |
| Transport         | train | bike | bus |

