.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-15::.
City: liverpool, nizza, marseilles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, metal, gospel
1. the fan metal is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the fan soul is between the person traveling to nizza and the fan gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| City   | nizza  | liverpool   | marseilles  |
| Music-Genre        | metal | soul | gospel |

