.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, singing
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, brown, blood-red
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who likes brown##2
3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Hobby      | singing | sudoku   | magic-tricks |
| Color   | blood-red  | lavender | brown   |

 